2012-10-05 Eugene Wissner <belka.ew@gmail.com>
	* Updated to 3.6.0
	* Replaced update-gtk-immodules-3.0 with slackware's original one
	* Added use_host_triplet_for_gtk_immodules.diff from slackware.
	Use /etc/gtk-3.0/$ARCH-slackware-linux instead of /etc/gtk-3.0/ for
	gtk.immodules.
	* Removed $PKG_DOCDIR because Slackware 14 uses gtk+3-${VERSION} directory
	for the documentation
	* Removed the setting of $host (it would be better if it would be set by
	dropline build system). Checking of the host value was commented out in
	Slackware 14.0
	* Added --enable-xkb option to configure, -DHOST c flag and make/make
	install option (everything from Slackware build script)
	* Fixed configuration files' paths
	* Enable to possibility to have the both x86 and x86-64 builds
	* Replaced desc with slackware's slack-desc from gtk+3

